## 3. Target Design

### 3.1 Proposed Architecture

The proposal is to migrate the BCD backend services â€” **API Gateway, Lambda functions (Queue Control, Decision Engine), and DynamoDB tables (CX Session Store)** â€” into their own dedicated AWS account, following the same pattern used for Personalization.

